\|\overset{\wedge}{w}\|^{2}=\left|\left|U\cdot\begin{bmatrix}a_{1}\\
\vdots\\
a_{r}\\
0\\
\vdots\\
0
\end{bmatrix}\right|\right|^{2}=\sum_{i=1}^{d}a_{i}^{2}\leq\sum_{i=1}^{r}a_{i}^{2}+\sum_{i=r+1}^{d}\beta_{i}^{2}=\|\bar{w}\|
\]

\end_inset


